{"sectionId":522,"sectionIdLiteral":"522","humanId":"lesson-117","volumeId":"workbook","locale":"en","titleInfo":{"ownlineNumber":"Lesson 117"},"annotation":"W-117","bodyHtml":"<div class=\"acim-text review-lesson review-3 lesson-117\"> <div data-paragraph-id=\"522#0\"><p class=\"p-review-intro\"><span data-sentence-id=\"522#0:1\">For morning and evening review:</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"522#1\"><p class=\"p-lesson-ref\"><span class=\"pnr\">1.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"522#1:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>(<span class=\"lref\">103</span>) <b>God, being Love, is also happiness.</b></span></p> <p class=\"p-prayer\"><span data-sentence-id=\"522#1:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Let me remember love is happiness, and nothing else brings joy.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"522#1:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>And so I choose to entertain no substitutes for love.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"522#2\"><p class=\"p-lesson-ref\"><span class=\"pnr\">2.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"522#2:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>(<span class=\"lref\">104</span>) <b>I seek but what belongs to me in truth.</b></span></p> <p class=\"p-prayer\"><span data-sentence-id=\"522#2:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span>Love is my heritage, and with it joy.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"522#2:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>These are the gifts my Father gave to me.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"522#2:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span>I would accept all that is mine in truth.</span></p></div> <div data-paragraph-id=\"522#3\"><p class=\"p-normal\"><span class=\"pnr\">3.</span> <span data-sentence-id=\"522#3:1\"><span class=\"snr noprint\">1</span>On the hour: <br/></span><span data-sentence-id=\"522#3:2\"><span class=\"snr\">2</span><b>God, being Love, is also happiness.</b></span></p> <p class=\"p-normal\"><span data-sentence-id=\"522#3:3\"><span class=\"snr\">3</span>On the half hour: <br/></span><span data-sentence-id=\"522#3:4\"><span class=\"snr\">4</span><b>I seek but what belongs to me in truth.</b></span></p></div> </div>","firstWords":"For morning and evening review: (103) God, being Love, is also happiness. Let me remember love is happiness, and nothing else brings joy. And so I choose to entertain no substitutes for love. (104) I","contentType":"acim-content","seoTitle":"Lesson 117: Review (103 and 104) | ACIM","seoDescription":"‚ú® A Course in Miracles with üéß Audio! Read and listen to Lesson¬†117 ‚ÄúReview (103 and 104)‚Äù: For morning and evening review: (103) God, being Love, is also happiness. Let me remember love‚Ä¶","desktopBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part I","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":403,"slugs":["lesson-1","nothing-i-see-means-anything"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Review III","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":515,"slugs":["review-iii","introduction"]}},{"label":"Lesson 117","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":522,"slugs":["review-iii","lesson-117"]}}],"mobileBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part I","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":403,"slugs":["lesson-1","nothing-i-see-means-anything"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Review III","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":515,"slugs":["review-iii","introduction"]}},{"label":"Lesson 117","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":522,"slugs":["review-iii","lesson-117"]}}],"seoBreadcrumbs":[{"label":"A Course in Miracles","leadsTo":"dashboard"},{"label":"Workbook","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":401,"slugs":["workbook","introduction"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Part I","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":403,"slugs":["lesson-1","nothing-i-see-means-anything"],"forceToc":true}},{"label":"Review III","leadsTo":{"locale":"en","sectionId":515,"slugs":["review-iii","introduction"]}},{"label":"Lesson 117","leadsTo":{"locale